The paper discusses the learning behavior of multi-agent networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses network topology and optimization, which are related to systems and control (cs.SY) and optimization and control (cs.MA). The paper also mentions Pareto optimal solutions, which are related to game theory and social choice (cs.GT). Finally, the paper discusses the diffusion of information over networks, which is related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
